[I] Rapid fuzzy string matching in Python using various string metrics

[T] RapidFuzz is a fast string matching library for Python and C++, which is
[T] using the string similarity calculations from FuzzyWuzzy.

[U] https://github.com/rapidfuzz/RapidFuzz

